Changes from 0.2 to 0.3 - released 2009/06/24

*General:
- added support for using the php native SOAP extension instead of eZSOAP classes: now WSDL is supported
- added 'iso8601' format for formatting datetime values: it is the standard format in xsd/wsdl
- added french, italian translation files (but the debugger is untranslated)
- access to proxy module can now be granted with a limitation on remote server
- compatibility with php 5.3: namespace is now a reserved word, we renamed all such methods and class memebers to ns
- updated the included phpxmlrpc/phpjsonrpc libs (used by the debugger) to the latest version

